sequenceDiagram
  actor Dev as Developer
  participant IDE as IDE/Agent <br/>(MCP Client)
  participant Lib as MCP Policy-Aware <br/>Package Discovery
  participant Docs as Contex7 <br/>Docs Service
  participant Repo as Project Repo

  Dev->>IDE: "Add file picker to UserProfileCard"
  IDE->>Repo: Check existing libs/patterns
  Repo-->>IDE: No file picker found

  IDE->>Lib: Search for suitable file picker package
  Lib-->>IDE: Candidate library <br/>(name, version, link)

  IDE->>Docs: Fetch official docs <br/>(install, API, examples)
  Docs-->>IDE: Installation steps + code samples

  IDE->>IDE: Augment context with docs & examples
  IDE-->>Dev: Proposed diff <br/>(imports, usage, install steps)
  Dev->>IDE: Accept / Modify / Reject
